text: Campagne-lès-Boulonnais is a commune in the Pas-de-Calais department in the Hauts-de-France region of France. ==Geography== A village situated some 16 miles (25 km) southeast of Boulogne-sur-Mer on the D92 road. ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Pas-de-Calais department ==References== * INSEE commune file Campagnelesboulonnais
title: Campagne-lès-Boulonnais
